    "description": "在《Simpler Times》中，你将扮演塔伊娜，她正准备离开童年的家，并开启她生命中的下一章。重温她的回忆，了解她如何成长为一个富有创造力和表达力的人。这是一种能让人沉思舒适的体验。没有分数、没有计时器、没有战斗、没有失败，也没有焦虑。只有放松。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四个季节，四个记录</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/16472a58c0afc4ae5feecaa1119d899f.poster.avif?t=1747072271\" width=630 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/16472a58c0afc4ae5feecaa1119d899f.webm?t=1747072271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/16472a58c0afc4ae5feecaa1119d899f.mp4?t=1747072271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>《Simpler Times》发生在塔伊娜的童年卧室里。在这里，你可以听音乐、绘画、观察大自然、拍照、翻阅书籍、阅读笔记并解决谜题。每个物品都有一个故事要讲述。游戏跨越了十年的时间，有四个不同的时刻可供探索，每一个都以不同的季节作为主题。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >按自己的节奏进行游戏</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/9b930a37acea96da2fc08040a804b7a6.poster.avif?t=1747072271\" width=630 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/9b930a37acea96da2fc08040a804b7a6.webm?t=1747072271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/9b930a37acea96da2fc08040a804b7a6.mp4?t=1747072271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>在《Simpler Times》中，你可以探索塔伊娜过去的每一章，游戏内没有设置计时器或失败状态以增加玩家不必要的压力。通过仔细观察和内省，细腻的叙述逐渐展开，奖励那些拥抱《Simpler Times》反思性质的人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >悠扬的音乐，让人心旷神怡</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/b9e4463fe1a934aa6d3fb30150d72ae5.poster.avif?t=1747072271\" width=630 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/b9e4463fe1a934aa6d3fb30150d72ae5.webm?t=1747072271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812210/extras/b9e4463fe1a934aa6d3fb30150d72ae5.mp4?t=1747072271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>音乐是《Simpler Times》的心灵中心，塔伊娜通过在唱片机上旋转唱片来重温她的童年回忆。由George Pandrea创作的出色低保真原声配乐，与塔伊娜现实世界的配音演员Maeve Kroeger的抒情诗一起，为游戏增添了独特的韵味。相信我们，你会一遍又一遍地聆听这些充满韵味的曲调。",
